ChangeList.Description: Added new PrintJob.Create [delegated permission](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/permissions-reference#universal-print-permissions).
Added new PrinterShare.ReadBasic.All [delegated permission](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/permissions-reference#universal-print-permissions).
Changed **floorNumber** (Edm.Int) property on [printerLocation](/graph/api/resources/printerlocation?view=graph-rest-beta) resource to **floor** (Edm.String).
Changed **roomNumber** (Edm.Int) property on [printerLocation](/graph/api/resources/printerlocation?view=graph-rest-beta) resource to **roomName** (Edm.String).

Added the [update configuration](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/printjob-update-configuration?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [printJob](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/printjob?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Changed type of allowedUsers relationship on [printerShare](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/printershare?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Changed type of allowedGroups relationship on [printerShare](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/printershare?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the `outputAreaAlmostFull` member to the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Added the `none` member to the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Added the `movingToPaused` member to the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Added the `shutdown` member to the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Added the `connectingToDevice` member to the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Added the `timedOut` member to the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Added the `stopping` member to the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Added the `stoppedPartially` member to the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Added the `tonerLow` member to the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Added the `tonerEmpty` member to the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Added the `spoolAreaFull` member to the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Added the `doorOpen` member to the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Added the `opticalPhotoConductorNearEndOfLife` member to the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Added the `opticalPhotoConductorLifeOver` member to the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Added the `developerLow` member to the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Added the `developerEmpty` member to the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Added the `interpreterResourceUnavailable` member to the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Removed the `disconnected` member from the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Removed the `queueFull` member from the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Removed the `outputAlmostFull` member from the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Removed the `unknownFutureValue` member from the **printerProcessingStateDetail** enumeration.
Added the **hasPhysicalDevice** property to the [printer](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/printer?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [abort](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/printjob-abort?view=graph-rest-beta) action to the [printJob](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/printjob?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the configuration property to the [redirect](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/printjob-redirect?view=graph-rest-beta) action on the [printJob](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/printjob?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added new permission requirements to: [Get printUsageSummaryByPrinter](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/printusagesummarybyprinter-get?view=graph-rest-beta), [getPrinterArchivedPrintJobs](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/reports-getprinterarchivedprintjobs?view=graph-rest-beta), [List dailyPrintUsageSummariesByPrinter](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/reportroot-list-dailyprintusagesummariesbyprinter?view=graph-rest-beta), [List monthlyPrintUsageSummariesByPrinter](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/reportroot-list-monthlyprintusagesummariesbyprinter?view=graph-rest-beta), [Get printUsageSummaryByUser](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/printusagesummarybyuser-get?view=graph-rest-beta), [getUserArchivedPrintJobs](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/reports-getuserarchivedprintjobs?view=graph-rest-beta), [getGroupArchivedPrintJobs](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/reports-getgrouparchivedprintjobs?view=graph-rest-beta), [List dailyPrintUsageSummariesByUser](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/reportroot-list-dailyprintusagesummariesbyuser?view=graph-rest-beta), [List monthlyPrintUsageSummariesByUser](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/reportroot-list-monthlyprintusagesummariesbyuser?view=graph-rest-beta)
Removed the **allowedUsers** property on the [printer](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/printer?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Removed the **allowedGroups** property on the [printer](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/printer?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
